text: The 1930 George Washington Colonials football team was an American football team that represented George Washington University as an independent during the 1930 college football season. In its second season under head coach Jim Pixlee, the team compiled a 4–4–1 record. ==Schedule== ==References== George Washington Category:George Washington Colonials football seasons George Washington Colonials football
